        "subject": "LU-957 scrub: API changes for OI Scrub",
        "message": "LU-957 scrub: API changes for OI Scrub\n\nThe main changes include:\n\n1) new parameter \"lu_object_hint\" for MD/DT name lookup\n   and object find, to transfer object local identifier\n   and some other information.\n\n2) new OSD iterator interface: dt_it_ops::set(),\n   for adjusting iteration parameters and events\n   notification during the iteration.\n\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ic6d0d7af676ee276652287296972cf38f278db02\n"
      },
